rComments: Very helpful prof; he demonstrates immense knowledge of the subject and increases interest in the subject matter; his lectures are very long-winded and could be much shorter; fair marker.

Wonderful professor. He is so kind and you can tell he is interested in what he teaches. I love his classes! He makes archaeology interesting and fun to learn. He is a fair marker and I would love to take another class with him again.
One of my favorite professors; is a tough but fair marker, and makes archaeology more interesting that I ever thought it would be
Amazing Prof! Very clear and fair marker.
Amazing prof! Very entertaining, knew what he was talking about and passionate about the material.
